race.comment: GOLDSTAR PRADA (2) is a talented type and proved too classy last time to win by 2 lengths at this track in a handy 36.73 beating COOL IT. Expected to go well again. FLYING ERNESTO (4) turned in a solid run last start over 642m at this track finishing 4th and beaten only 5 lengths (37.06). Has placed several times at this track. Cannot be left out. ALL OUT FIRE (1) has some solid form under his belt and proved too classy last time to win by a neck at this track in a handy 36.56 beating RESILIENT. Winner at his latest appearance in the quickest time on the card. Leading chance again. RESILIENT (7) must be included on latest effort.
